      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey im prepping for a debate tournament and im kinda stuck. if u had to pick which side of the illegal immigration debate is actually more morally defensible, which one would it be? like the border security argument or the humanitarian asylum one? i need to know which side has the stronger moral ground so i can plan my opening.",
